      "created": 1764801063,
      "updated": 1764801063
    },
    {
      "id": "6930ba276eb406000000afdea1",
      "text": "第49週: 日月火水[[木]]金土",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1764801064,
      "updated": 1764801064
    },
    {
      "id": "6930ba276eb40600000079c4ae",
      "text": "2025年 92.60％経過",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1764801064,
      "updated": 1764801064
    },
    {
      "id": "6930ba276eb406000000e1ced4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1764801064,
      "updated": 1764801064
    },
    {
      "id": "6930c897000000000036fc52",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1764804759,
      "updated": 1764804760
    },
    {
      "id": "6930c897000000000036fc53",
      "text": "[koyoshi.icon]",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1764804760,
      "updated": 1764804764
    },
    {
      "id": "6930c89d000000000036fc54",
      "text": " おはいおござます",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1764804766,
      "updated": 1764804781
    },
    {
      "id": "6930c8b0000000000036fc55",
      "text": "  おや、この時間（8:33）なのに一番乗り？",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1764804785,
      "updated": 1764804838
    },
    {
      "id": "69312102000000000028f8ec",
      "text": " お昼に食べた「[かぼちゃコロッケ]」が いつもと違う味だった",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1764827394,
      "updated": 1764853165
    },
    {
      "id": "69312104000000000028f8ed",
      "text": "  「まずい」とか「やばい」とか、そういう意味ではない",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1764827397,
      "updated": 1764827404
    },
    {
      "id": "69312104000000000028f8ee",
      "text": "  思ってた かぼちゃの味ではなく、さつまいもとか栗とかの味がした",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1764827397,
      "updated": 1764827407
    },
    {
      "id": "69312104000000000028f8ef",
      "text": "  確認してみたら「栗かぼちゃ」のコロッケだった",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1764827397,
      "updated": 1764827408
    },
    {
      "id": "6930ba276eb4060000007f7024",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1764801064,
      "updated": 1764801064
    },
    {
      "id": "6930cf920000000000c29e6d",
      "text": "[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1764806549,
      "updated": 1764806549
    },
    {
      "id": "6930cf920000000000c29e6e",
      "text": "\tアドベントカレンダー書いた",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1764806549,
      "updated": 1764806556
    },
    {
      "id": "6930cf9a0000000000c29e6f",
      "text": "\t\t[ランニングマンはいいぞおじさん「ランニングマンはいいぞ」]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1764806556,
      "updated": 1764806557
    },
    {
      "id": "69310f270000000000be78ca",
      "text": "\t\t👏[mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1764822824,
      "updated": 1764822827
    },
    {
      "id": "6930d36b00000000002f527a",
      "text": "\t[「KPIは睡眠時間」──オードリー・タンに聞く、日本企業の生産性が上がらない根本原因 - ITmedia ビジネスオンライン https://www.itmedia.co.jp/business/articles/2512/03/news042.html]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1764807533,
      "updated": 1764817954
    },
    {
      "id": "6930fc200000000000d73154",
      "text": "\t\t会員限定記事なので見れないけど、いいなそれ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1764817956,
      "updated": 1764817963
    },
    {
      "id": "6930fc280000000000d73155",
      "text": "\t\t健康というか「良い状態」のキープをモニタリングする",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1764817963,
      "updated": 1764817981
    },
    {
      "id": "6930fc3b0000000000d73156",
      "text": "\t\t\tが、それだとディストピアっぽくなっちゃうので、「良い状態を阻害する因子」をモニタリングする",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1764817982,
      "updated": 1764817996
    },
    {
      "id": "6930fc4a0000000000d73157",
      "text": "\t\t\tthoughtworks社の[Engineering Effectiveness]の考え",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1764817999,
      "updated": 1764818012
    },
    {
      "id": "6930fc5a0000000000d73158",
      "text": "\t\t\t僕は[/neoterizer/管理3.0]として整理",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1764818012,
      "updated": 1764818022
    },
    {
      "id": "6930fc7a0000000000d73159",
      "text": "\t\tタンはわかりやすいたとえや例が上手い",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1764818044,
      "updated": 1764818055
    },
    {
      "id": "6930fca80000000000d7315a",
      "text": "\t\t\t逆にどうして俺は[睡眠時間をKPIにする]という発想を出すことができないのか",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1764818091,
      "updated": 1764855550
    },
    {
      "id": "6930fc1f0000000000d73153",
      "text": "\t[gogh気になるンゴ]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1764817953,
      "updated": 1764839743
    },
    {
      "id": "693151320000000000322009",
      "text": "\t\t[gogh]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1764839731,
      "updated": 1764839735
    },
    {
      "id": "693150400000000000322001",
      "text": "\t\t[【 作業 / 雑談 】みんなで作業 in gogh #2【 羽澄さひろ┆VEE 】 - YouTube https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bCVyTHMYyLQ]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1764839489,
      "updated": 1764839495
    },
    {
      "id": "693150470000000000322002",
      "text": "\t\t[Teracy]みたいなやつか",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1764839496,
      "updated": 1764839583
    },
    {
      "id": "6931509e0000000000322003",
      "text": "\t\t[作業集中支援アプリ「gogh」に注目している｜ささもと https://note.com/ssmt_nt/n/ned49603679e3]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1764839583,
      "updated": 1764839583
    },
    {
      "id": "6931509f0000000000322004",
      "text": "\t\t\tコミュニケーション機能が意図的に削がれてて一緒にいるくらいしかできない感じ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1764839583,
      "updated": 1764839597
    },
    {
      "id": "6931503a0000000000322000",
      "text": "\t\t[gogh - YouTube https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=gogh]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1764839483,
      "updated": 1764839669
    },
    {
      "id": "693150f50000000000322006",
      "text": "\t\tふうむ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1764839669,
      "updated": 1764839705
    },
    {
      "id": "693151180000000000322007",
      "text": "\t\t\t配信してるVのとこに入るのはさすがになー",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1764839705,
      "updated": 1764839714
    },
    {
      "id": "69316e2c00000000009a4eca",
      "text": "\t\tいいぞ[caki.icon][基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1764847148,
      "updated": 1764847440
    },
    {
      "id": "693150f40000000000322005",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1764839669,
      "updated": 1764839669
    },
    {
      "id": "6930d36b00000000002f527b",
      "text": "[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1764807533,
      "updated": 1764807534
    },
    {
      "id": "6930d36c00000000002f527c",
      "text": "\tず が つう 気味",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1764807534,
      "updated": 1764807565
    },
    {
      "id": "6930ba276eb406000000f1b7e9",
      "text": "　　おだ　いじ　に[nishio.icon][taktamur.icon][sta.icon][mtane0412.icon][W7kA9pX2.icon][suto3.icon][Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "644fa04c7142e4001b4b5d09",
      "created": 1764801064,
      "updated": 1764847903
    },
    {
      "id": "693145610000000000e90f95",
      "text": "　　\t🙏[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1764836706,
      "updated": 1764836713
    },
    {
      "id": "6931456a0000000000e90f96",
      "text": "　寝込んでおり 候",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1764836715,
      "updated": 1764836730
    },
    {
      "id": "69314cd200000000000e7894",
      "text": "　\t両頬と手の指先がピリピリする",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1764838610,
      "updated": 1764838619
    },
    {
      "id": "69314c9100000000000e7892",
      "text": "　鳥に挟まれると裏返ります",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1764838546,
      "updated": 1764838552
    },
    {
      "id": "69316cf40000000000ce15ba",
      "text": "　\t→[鳥に挟まれて裏返った絵][nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764846836,
      "updated": 1764846844
    },
    {
      "id": "69314c9900000000000e7893",
      "text": "　[阿波踊り 親鳥！阿波踊り 雛鳥！]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764838554,
      "updated": 1764846940
    },
    {
      "id": "6930d45b00000000006e5ac4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764807771,
      "updated": 1764807771
    },
    {
      "id": "6930d45b00000000006e5ac5",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764807771,
      "updated": 1764807774
    },
    {
      "id": "6930d45e00000000006e5ac6",
      "text": "　さむ　い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764807774,
      "updated": 1764807783
    },
    {
      "id": "6930e1c100000000006e5ac8",
      "text": "　https://x.com/kamoshika_en/status/1996170472468451668?s=46&t=gkSZtjGEtUZPO0JCzBxCBw",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764811201,
      "updated": 1764811203
    },
    {
      "id": "6930e1c400000000006e5ac9",
      "text": "　　これをみて「だが」が間違ってると言ってくる人がいることが面白かった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764811204,
      "updated": 1764811231
    },
    {
      "id": "6930e7060000000000e23ca1",
      "text": "　　「だが」の意図を理解した時にアハ体験的な面白さ。いいオチ[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1764812549,
      "updated": 1764812790
    },
    {
      "id": "6930e1df00000000006e5aca",
      "text": "　鳥に挟まれている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764811232,
      "updated": 1764811251
    },
    {
      "id": "6930d46700000000006e5ac7",
      "text": "\t本日の火遊び",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764807783,
      "updated": 1764816656
    },
    {
      "id": "6930f70f0000000000db2c9d",
      "text": "\t\tベランダでお湯を沸かす、タンブラー1杯分",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764816656,
      "updated": 1764816676
    },
    {
      "id": "6930f7230000000000db2c9e",
      "text": "\t\t開始からお湯を得るまで15分、割り箸2→[杉の間伐材]2→割り箸1",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764816676,
      "updated": 1764816708
    },
    {
      "id": "6930f74c0000000000db2c9f",
      "text": "\t\tタンブラーに移した後の水温が85度",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764816716,
      "updated": 1764816740
    },
    {
      "id": "6930f7810000000000db2ca0",
      "text": "\t\t多分燃料を増やしても火力がそんなに上がらない(炎がはみ出してしまう)から、沸騰させたいなら間伐材x3を時間をあけて投入する必要がありそう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764816769,
      "updated": 1764816825
    },
    {
      "id": "6930f8d30000000000db2ca3",
      "text": "\t\t\t85度で十分かもしれない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764817107,
      "updated": 1764817114
    },
    {
      "id": "6931905500000000004ac69b",
      "text": "\t\t\tコーヒーとかにちょうど良さそう[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1764855891,
      "updated": 1764855897
    },
    {
      "id": "6930f7b80000000000db2ca1",
      "text": "\t\t間伐材の投入間隔の時間は測ってなかった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764816825,
      "updated": 1764816907
    },
    {
      "id": "6930de050000000000e23c9e",
      "text": "\t[堂々と盛大に火遊びができるプレイス]の調査を進めています",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1764810245,
      "updated": 1764853185
    },
    {
      "id": "693149740000000000c0f732",
      "text": "\t\t現在の有力候補",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764837748,
      "updated": 1764837783
    },
    {
      "id": "693149970000000000c0f733",
      "text": "\t\t\t[/nishio/自然人村（東京・あきる野市）]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764837783,
      "updated": 1764837784
    },
    {
      "id": "693149980000000000c0f734",
      "text": "\t\t\t[/nishio/青野原 野呂ロッジキャンプ場]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764837784,
      "updated": 1764837789
    },
    {
      "id": "6931499d0000000000c0f735",
      "text": "\t\tタカオネは一回行って失敗したのと、そもそも焚き火ができるプレースが建物の中庭で、飲み物持ち込み禁止とか制約が大きくてげんなりした",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764837790,
      "updated": 1764837823
    },
    {
      "id": "69316c8e00000000009c03d0",
      "text": "\tnano banana「[鳥に挟まれて裏返った絵]です」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764846737,
      "updated": 1764846774
    },
    {
      "id": "69316ca700000000009c03d1",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/fef77f0696166d390d9de61e82dd56ce]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764846762,
      "updated": 1764846764
    },
    {
      "id": "69316ca900000000009c03d2",
      "text": "\t\t入力された絵の再現は上手なのに「裏返る」の解釈はこうなのか〜",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764846764,
      "updated": 1764848493
    },
    {
      "id": "6931495e0000000000c0f731",
      "text": "\t\t試しにiconにしてたけどそんな面白くないし、何より[他人のアイデンティディの一部を自分のアイデンティティに取り込むのは気持ちが悪い]ので撤回する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1764837727,
      "updated": 1764947206
    },
    {
      "id": "6931a34b00000000009c03da",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764860747,
      "updated": 1764860748
    },
    {
      "id": "6930de060000000000e23c9f",
      "text": "[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1764810245,
      "updated": 1764810246
    },
    {
      "id": "6930de080000000000e23ca0",
      "text": " さんぽぽ。",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1764810247,
      "updated": 1764810261
    },
    {
      "id": "6930fb5700000000005a5937",
      "text": " 天気も良いし仕事も忙しくないのだけど、[むなしい気分]が出てきてる。",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1764817750,
      "updated": 1764818329
    },
    {
      "id": "6930fb7100000000005a5938",
      "text": "  まぁ受け流しておこう。",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1764817776,
      "updated": 1764817784
    },
    {
      "id": "6930fba000000000005a5939",
      "text": "  こーゆー日は、頭を使わずに体を動かす事をしてれば良い。",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1764817823,
      "updated": 1764817852
    },
    {
      "id": "6930fe9800000000006fe695",
      "text": " 腰にも違和感を発見",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1764818583,
      "updated": 1764818592
    },
    {
      "id": "6930fea200000000006fe696",
      "text": "  今の気分は肉体起因だなこれ。",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1764818593,
      "updated": 1764818606
    },
    {
      "id": "6930feb800000000006fe697",
      "text": "  気温差にやられてる。",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1764818615,
      "updated": 1764818624
    },
    {
      "id": "6931125400000000007738f5",
      "text": " 昨日、[scrapbox-duplicator]が動いてないかも？と[書いた https://scrapbox.io/villagepump/2025%2F12%2F03#692fc9de0000000000bd6a36]けど、ちゃんと動いていた",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1764823637,
      "updated": 1764826773
    },
    {
      "id": "6931127000000000007738f7",
      "text": " \t自分が[/taktamur]のソート順を「閲覧数」のままにしてて、更新されてるのに気づかなかっただけ。",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1764823665,
      "updated": 1764823713
    },
    {
      "id": "6930d44d00000000006e5ac3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1764807758,
      "updated": 1764807758
    },
    {
      "id": "6930e603000000000013f045",
      "text": "[mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1764812292,
      "updated": 1764812292
    },
    {
      "id": "6930e604000000000013f046",
      "text": " [https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-025-09823-0 Video-call glitches trigger uncanniness and harm consequential life outcomes | Nature]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1764812292,
      "updated": 1764812296
    },
    {
      "id": "6930e607000000000013f047",
      "text": "  [ビデオ通話]の品質の低さが不気味さを喚起して対人評価を下げる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1764812296,
      "updated": 1764853195
    },
    {
      "id": "6930e615000000000013f04a",
      "text": " 　確かに仕事だと通信回線もマイクもゴミレベルな人しかいない",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1764812310,
      "updated": 1764812323
    },
    {
      "id": "6930e620000000000013f04b",
      "text": " 　　そういう人たちがやっぱり対面だよね〜となるのは自然",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1764812320,
      "updated": 1764812336
    },
    {
      "id": "6930ef100000000000723611",
      "text": " [Nani翻訳]とてもよい",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1764814609,
      "updated": 1764815209
    },
    {
      "id": "6930ef150000000000723612",
      "text": " 　このクオリティを見せられると僕の考えた最強の◯◯を作りたくなってくる",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1764814613,
      "updated": 1764814632
    },
    {
      "id": "69310ed10000000000be78c7",
      "text": " ちゃんとソフトウェア・エンジニアリングを学びたくなってきた",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1764822738,
      "updated": 1764822748
    },
    {
      "id": "69310edb0000000000be78c8",
      "text": " 　Claude Codeのせいで触れる領域が増えてしまった",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1764822748,
      "updated": 1764822772
    },
    {
      "id": "6930e608000000000013f048",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1764812297,
      "updated": 1764812299
    },
    {
      "id": "6930ea140000000000aadf98",
      "text": "[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1764813330,
      "updated": 1764813341
    },
    {
      "id": "6930ea200000000000aadf9d",
      "text": " [Googleカレンダーのタスク]が時間幅を持つようになってる",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1764813342,
      "updated": 1764855994
    },
    {
      "id": "6930ea150000000000aadf99",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/e798c013b43cec5d81841814e4b5812d]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1764813331,
      "updated": 1764813498
    },
    {
      "id": "6930eae70000000000aadf9f",
      "text": "  今まで開始時刻のみ指定できた気がする",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1764813541,
      "updated": 1764813541
    },
    {
      "id": "6930eb2d0000000000aadfa1",
      "text": "  でもデフォルトでは[予定なし]扱いのようだ",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1764813611,
      "updated": 1764813622
    },
    {
      "id": "69316c3200000000004ac69a",
      "text": " Slackのcanvasをmarkdownでエクスポートしたい",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1764846640,
      "updated": 1764846654
    },
    {
      "id": "6930ea1a0000000000aadf9b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1764813336,
      "updated": 1764813336
    },
    {
      "id": "6930efec000000000019e51d",
      "text": "[W7kA9pX2.icon]",
      "userId": "644fa04c7142e4001b4b5d09",
      "created": 1764814829,
      "updated": 1764814830
    },
    {
      "id": "6930efee000000000019e51e",
      "text": "　水道水の件[消費生活センター]に連絡したりなどしたがまとめると「管理会社の領分なんで〜」て感じでしょんもり",
      "userId": "644fa04c7142e4001b4b5d09",
      "created": 1764814831,
      "updated": 1764814999
    },
    {
      "id": "6930f1f40000000000e23ca3",
      "text": "　  そんなー[taktamur.icon][nishio.icon][nomadoor.icon][yosider.icon][Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1764815347,
      "updated": 1764847959
    },
    {
      "id": "6931858e000000000023c064",
      "text": "　  🍵[着地鳩.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1764853134,
      "updated": 1764853144
    },
    {
      "id": "6930f038000000000019e51f",
      "text": "　　市販の簡易水質検査キット買ってみて問題なかったら[W7kA9pX2.icon]がおかしいてことで丸くしてヤバイ結果でたらもっかい管理会社に連絡しよ",
      "userId": "644fa04c7142e4001b4b5d09",
      "created": 1764814905,
      "updated": 1764814983
    },
    {
      "id": "6931368f000000000047140b",
      "text": "　お米屋さん？からお正月のお餅はいかがですか？のチラシが着ててなんか良かった",
      "userId": "644fa04c7142e4001b4b5d09",
      "created": 1764832912,
      "updated": 1764833040
    },
    {
      "id": "69313958000000000047140e",
      "text": "　　箱に雑然と入れられた画質の粗い餅、良い",
      "userId": "644fa04c7142e4001b4b5d09",
      "created": 1764833625,
      "updated": 1764833661
    },
    {
      "id": "693136b8000000000047140c",
      "text": "　　去年はなかった思う",
      "userId": "644fa04c7142e4001b4b5d09",
      "created": 1764832952,
      "updated": 1764832961
    },
    {
      "id": "693136c3000000000047140d",
      "text": "　　お売りください！的なチラシばかりでチラシお断り😤的なのポストに貼るか悩んでたけどこゆのはなんか良いから着てほしいな",
      "userId": "644fa04c7142e4001b4b5d09",
      "created": 1764832963,
      "updated": 1764833035
    },
    {
      "id": "6930ea150000000000aadf9a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1764813331,
      "updated": 1764813331
    },
    {
      "id": "6930f9490000000000c1f6e8",
      "text": "[nomadoor.icon]",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1764817324,
      "updated": 1764817324
    },
    {
      "id": "6930f94a0000000000c1f6e9",
      "text": "　最近PCが良く落ちるので中見てみたらすごいホコリだった…",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1764817324,
      "updated": 1764817360
    },
    {
      "id": "6930f96e0000000000c1f6ea",
      "text": "　　掃除したら今のところ落ちてないので、静電気だったのかな？",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1764817360,
      "updated": 1764817377
    },
    {
      "id": "6930f9b90000000000c1f6ec",
      "text": "　　PCケースを入れるケースが欲しいですね(排熱)",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1764817435,
      "updated": 1764817445
    },
    {
      "id": "6930f9810000000000c1f6eb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1764817379,
      "updated": 1764817387
    },
    {
      "id": "6931077d0000000000eec2d8",
      "text": "[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1764820863,
      "updated": 1764820863
    },
    {
      "id": "6931077f0000000000eec2d9",
      "text": " 12月の洗礼を受けている",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1764820864,
      "updated": 1764820873
    },
    {
      "id": "6931078f0000000000eec2da",
      "text": "  さむすぎてぽんぺ",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1764820879,
      "updated": 1764820935
    },
    {
      "id": "693107930000000000eec2db",
      "text": "  10月くらいに衣替えしそびれ、服の8割が半袖",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1764820884,
      "updated": 1764820914
    },
    {
      "id": "693108010000000000eec2dc",
      "text": " 半年くらい音信不通だった中国の文通友と連絡がつき、うれしい",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1764820994,
      "updated": 1764821017
    },
    {
      "id": "693108350000000000061d36",
      "text": "  いいね[taktamur.icon][W7kA9pX2.icon][Hiro Aki.icon][yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "644fa04c7142e4001b4b5d09",
      "created": 1764821044,
      "updated": 1764856026
    },
    {
      "id": "6930f9480000000000c1f6e7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1764817322,
      "updated": 1764817322
    },
    {
      "id": "69310af60000000000f0fcd6",
      "text": "[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1764821749,
      "updated": 1764821751
    },
    {
      "id": "693e7ea60000000000bfced6",
      "text": " [Building index]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1765703334,
      "updated": 1765703340
    },
    {
      "id": "693122480000000000f0fcda",
      "text": "　[Excelの妙な使いづらさ]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1764827719,
      "updated": 1764827733
    },
    {
      "id": "693122570000000000f0fcdb",
      "text": "　　階層管理してフィルターしても見づらいとか",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1764827734,
      "updated": 1764827753
    },
    {
      "id": "69317dc90000000000edd56f",
      "text": "　[CVE-2025-55182]がまずいという話を聞いた",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1764851143,
      "updated": 1764851178
    },
    {
      "id": "69310af60000000000f0fcd7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1764821749,
      "updated": 1764821749
    },
    {
      "id": "693171820000000000923a00",
      "text": "[Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1764848002,
      "updated": 1764848005
    },
    {
      "id": "693171840000000000923a01",
      "text": "\t出張はやはり嫌なものだ",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1764848005,
      "updated": 1764848013
    },
    {
      "id": "6931718c0000000000923a02",
      "text": "\t\t長距離運転マジメンドクセ",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1764848013,
      "updated": 1764848019
    },
    {
      "id": "693171970000000000923a03",
      "text": "\t\t片道340kmだったっけ、それくらい",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1764848024,
      "updated": 1764848051
    },
    {
      "id": "693171b20000000000923a04",
      "text": "\t\t北海道民からすればボチボチ程度の距離になったりするのかな",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1764848051,
      "updated": 1764848061
    },
    {
      "id": "6931916400000000004ac69d",
      "text": "\t\t大変すぎる[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1764856162,
      "updated": 1764856165
    },
    {
      "id": "693171e60000000000923a05",
      "text": "\t自衛隊の駐屯地の隣を通る際、敷地内の事務所っぽい建屋に隣接する駐車場へ、どこにでもありそうな軽自動車と装輪車が仲良く並んで駐車してた",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1764848103,
      "updated": 1764848162
    },
    {
      "id": "693172220000000000923a06",
      "text": "\t\t日常的な物と非日常的な物が並んでてなんかギャップが良いなと",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1764848162,
      "updated": 1764848275
    },
    {
      "id": "6931718200000000009239ff",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1764848002,
      "updated": 1764848002
    },
    {
      "id": "693183da000000000023c058",
      "text": "[着地鳩.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1764852698,
      "updated": 1764852700
    },
    {
      "id": "693e7e280000000000bfced4",
      "text": " [星霜の心理士]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1765703207,
      "updated": 1765703215
    },
    {
      "id": "693186350000000000959f9b",
      "text": " 月を天笠とする歌が万葉集にあったなあ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1764853301,
      "updated": 1764853644
    },
    {
      "id": "693186eb0000000000959fa1",
      "text": "  [ひさかたの天ゆく月を網に刺しわご大王は蓋にせり]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1764853484,
      "updated": 1764853647
    },
    {
      "id": "693186ec0000000000959fa2",
      "text": "   [歌詳細 | 万葉百科 奈良県立万葉文化館 https://manyo-hyakka.pref.nara.jp/db/detailLink?cls=db_manyo&pkey=240]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1764853485,
      "updated": 1764856189
    },
    {
      "id": "693186fa0000000000959fa3",
      "text": "   あら人麻呂歌",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1764853499,
      "updated": 1764853655
    },
    {
      "id": "693188070000000000959fa5",
      "text": " [#創作漫画 パットおじさんのいた夏 - ジョハンのマンガ #ギャグ #真理 - pixiv https://www.pixiv.net/artworks/137830489]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1764853770,
      "updated": 1764856193
    },
    {
      "id": "693188260000000000959fb5",
      "text": " 12月のおともに[シュトーレン]を手配した",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1764853799,
      "updated": 1764856268
    },
    {
      "id": "693188260000000000959fb6",
      "text": "  街のパン屋さんによる手作りで数量限定、現在制作中とのこと。できたら連絡をくれる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1764853799,
      "updated": 1764853799
    },
    {
      "id": "6931868b0000000000959f9c",
      "text": " [月の歌]は膨大にあるので各々好きな歌を探すといい",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1764853388,
      "updated": 1764856276
    },
    {
      "id": "693186a30000000000959f9d",
      "text": "  [月々に月見る月は多けれど月見る月はこの月の月]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1764853412,
      "updated": 1764856304
    },
    {
      "id": "693186a80000000000959f9f",
      "text": "   [月見る月はこの月の月 | 小倉山荘（ブランドサイト） | 京都せんべい おかき専門店 長岡京 小倉山荘 https://ogurasansou.jp.net/columns/arakaruta/2018/01/23/1550/]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1764853417,
      "updated": 1764856195
    },
    {
      "id": "693186b20000000000959fa0",
      "text": "   何の何に収録されているのだろうか",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1764853429,
      "updated": 1764853436
    },
    {
      "id": "693184a5000000000023c05f",
      "text": " [［第1話］ガチャンキイ - 下元朗 | 少年ジャンプ＋ https://shonenjumpplus.com/episode/17107094912077655356]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1764852902,
      "updated": 1764856198
    },
    {
      "id": "693184a7000000000023c060",
      "text": "  [ガチャンキイ]まあまあ注目しているのだが、周りに読んでる人が少ない",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1764852903,
      "updated": 1764853634
    },
    {
      "id": "693184b9000000000023c061",
      "text": "   4話のオチが良かった",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1764852922,
      "updated": 1764852930
    },
    {
      "id": "693187a50000000000959fa4",
      "text": " かつて教えを乞うた人の葬式からはや一年以上が過ぎ、[師のいない世]を生きているのだなあと思う時がふとある",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1764853669,
      "updated": 1764856314
    },
    {
      "id": "693185df0000000000959f99",
      "text": " スポティファイの年度まとめが来ていて、例年通りZUNTATAが上位であった",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1764853216,
      "updated": 1764853239
    },
    {
      "id": "6931883a0000000000959fe4",
      "text": " 今日は満月だが寒い",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1764853818,
      "updated": 1764853818
    },
    {
      "id": "6931883a0000000000959fe5",
      "text": "  句でもよむか……",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1764853818,
      "updated": 1764853818
    },
    {
      "id": "6931883a0000000000959fe6",
      "text": "  オリオンの頭の上の月丸し",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1764853818,
      "updated": 1764853818
    },
    {
      "id": "693183da000000000023c059",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1764852698,
      "updated": 1764852698
    },
    {
      "id": "6931a013000000000017076c",
      "text": "[カイト.icon]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1764859925,
      "updated": 1764859927
    },
    {
      "id": "6931a016000000000017076e",
      "text": "\t2.5日寝込んでいた",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1764859928,
      "updated": 1764859966
    },
    {
      "id": "6931a03c000000000017076f",
